title: JPLL Self-Guided Tour 2025
content:
Welcome to J. Paul Leonard Library! We are glad you're here. JPLL is located on the central campus of San Francisco State University. The Main Library occupies the ground through fourth floors, while the fifth and sixth floors house the Sutro Library, part of the California State Library. Learn about Library spaces and services on this self-guided tour. This tour is best viewed on a mobile device.
